# CodeClutch ğŸ§ ğŸ’»

CodeClutch is an **AI-powered interview preparation platform** built for software engineering students.  
It analyzes resumes, generates tailored interview questions, and evaluates answers with structured feedback â€” simulating a real technical interview experience.

