## âœ¨ Features

### ğŸ” Resume Analysis
- Paste resume text or upload a PDF
- Extracts:
  - Skills
  - Projects
  - Experience level (beginner / intermediate / advanced)

### â“ Interview Question Generation
- Generates skill-based technical interview questions
- Includes varying difficulty levels
- Covers real-world engineering concepts

### ğŸ“ Answer Evaluation
- AI evaluates user answers
- Provides:
  - Scores (0â€“10)
  - Per-question feedback
  - Strengths & improvement areas
  - Overall interview readiness summary

---

## ğŸ§± Tech Stack

### Frontend
- **React (Vite)**
- **JavaScript**
- **CSS**
- **Fetch API**

### Backend
- **FastAPI**
- **Pydantic**
- **Python**
- **OpenRouter (LLM Gateway)**  
  - Model: `nvidia/nemotron-3-nano-30b-a3b:free`
- **PyPDF2** (PDF parsing)

### Deployment
- **Frontend**: Vercel (recommended)
- **Backend**: Render

